{"tid":2368456,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"GOT7 7週年！　「見面會相擁哭泣」私下慶生歡笑…回憶片逼哭粉絲","createTime":"2021-01-16T08:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T15:03:10.000Z","uid":74065,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0c4854a2c16a7c667831b0aa96b4720c54fde144","tid":2368456,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T08:09:03.000Z","msg":"韓團GOT7日前確定各自有新的發展，全員都不留在原公司JYP娛樂，在合約到期日19日前迎來了出道7週年紀念，官方YouTube頻道也特別上傳了3分40秒珍貴回憶影片，讓粉絲忍不住流下淚水，Mark和Jackson（王嘉爾）也都特別發文感謝鳥寶寶們（官方粉絲名稱，아가새，IGOT7）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5399/d5399984.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5399%2Fd5399984.jpg&h=5523c10d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲GOT7於16日迎來七週年。（圖／翻攝自GOT7 YouTube）<br />\n<br />\nGOT7和JYP娛樂的合約即將在19日到期，雖然已經確定各奔東西，但官方YouTube頻道仍在相當有意義的7週年紀念日上傳了影片，可以看見他們高喊著「Come and Get it. GOT7」的口號打招呼，這幾年來的幕後花絮，每個人笑得燦爛並樂於其中，還有替彼此慶生的樣子，讓粉絲也忍不住聯想到當時看到這些片段的美好。<br />\n<br />\n影片中間也穿插著成員們剛出道和現在的畫面，最後也能看見GOT7首次舉辦見面會畫面，有粉絲替他們做的應援影片，也能看見成員們緊緊圍繞擁抱激動大哭的Jackson。在一起走過說長不長、說短不短的7年回憶最後，是GOT7喊著另一個經典口號「G.O.T.7.ZAI（GOT7加油，GOT7짜이）」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5399/5399985.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5399%2F5399985.jpg&h=d64ae35e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲JYP娛樂將GOT7出道多年的回憶剪成集錦。（圖／翻攝自GOT7 YouTube）<br />\n<br />\nMark在7週年這天特別發文：「7年前出道後，我們遇見了鳥寶寶們，謝謝你們陪我們走過這麼長一段時間，我們經歷了難過、幸福、生氣和歡笑的每一瞬間，這些全都成了美好回憶，未來和我們7個人一起創立更多美好回憶吧！謝謝鳥寶寶們～」附圖則是在南韓時間凌晨一點，衝上音源榜第一名的GOT7《謝謝》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5399/d5399986.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5399%2Fd5399986.jpg&h=1706c670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Mark發文。（圖／翻攝自Mark推特）<br />\n<br />\nJackson同樣也在推特寫下長文，感嘆時間過得這麼快，在南韓也待了10年多的時間：「真心感謝大家守護著我們成長，雖然我常說這句話，但我一定會更努力、展現更好更成熟的樣貌給大家看，這段時間總是疼愛著我的大家，真的謝謝你們，我一定會成為令大家驕傲的ARTIST。」其他成員則上傳著同一張7人背影照紀念。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5399/d5399987.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5399%2Fd5399987.jpg&h=dbacc6ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲GOT7上傳團體背影照紀念7週年。（圖／翻攝自GOT7成員IG、推特）<br />\n<br />\n▼7 Years With GOT7 愛 I GOT7。（影片／取自GOT7 YouTube，如遭刪除請見諒）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ipfqLJOydYg&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DipfqLJOydYg%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyB21egSez4RG9A7txFtatZY%3D&h=484f8c9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ipfqLJOydYg&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5bsiMiV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5bsiMiV.png&h=1979431d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.yesasia.ru/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/jyp-6jpg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yesasia.ru%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F06%2Fjyp-6jpg.jpg&h=d5e9c61d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後一條片 消費到最後"},{"pid":"326d9d6abac70eba0719f46aa71f09c9af4a5a2f","tid":2368456,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T08:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8499c34f34d12101ca9a0dd35f04971b6600ea26","tid":2368456,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T09:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c9591ff4f49ff588d3c2391568c84a8206b189","tid":2368456,"uid":234220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T15:03:10.000Z","msg":"但係今日隊長即刻開咗Twitter  好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}